text: Ærest cealdan broc scyt on Winburnan.
Of Winburnan on Mapoldorlea middeweardne.
Of Mapoldorlea innan eastlea.
Ut of eastlea on ðæt slæget linlæge mor.
Of ðam slægete in achirste on suðbeara suðeweardne.
Of suðbeara on linleaga mor.
Of linleage more on ða gemearcodan lindan.
Of ðære gemearcodan lindan on biricgaran be ðære norðeage.
Of biricgaran on ðone norðheal.
Of ðam norðheale on blacan dune.
Of ðære dune on ciddesbeara.
Of ciddesbeara on ða haran stanas.
Of ðam haran stanon andlang blacan dune ecge norð on ða haran apoldran.
Of ðære apoldran suð on ðone mere, on ðona haran wiðig.
Of ðam wiðige west on wænecan wyrð on ða beorgas.
Of wænecan wyrðe on suðheal suðeweardne.
Of ðan heale on holan broc.
Of ðan broce to ruwan leges gete.
Of ðan gete on hyrn.
Up andlang hyrn on ðone mearchagan.
Of ðam hagan on ðone readan weg.
Of ðam wege on heara Wulfrices gemære.
Of ðam landgemære andlang streames eft on cealdan broc.
Ðis ys ðæra VII hida landboc to Hortune ðe Cnut cining gebocode Bouige hys huskarle on ece yrfe.
Nu swutelað hit her ðæt Boui mid his scette awerede ðæt land and forescet on ealre scire gewitnysse.
